moji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3aef27524796596c5c82e34171841854538bc29","tid":2293661,"uid":270206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb36a372c34b9ebd5f6897fa35dd46b75d2aff0","tid":2293661,"uid":5721,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"681ddf6347728200df17e90d2488c06b7d833db7","tid":2293661,"uid":270206,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"袁國勇終於說對了<br />\n<br />\n我這次極之認同袁國勇這句哲學家的話：「強制檢驗不是侵犯人權。」<br />\n<br />\n要侵犯人權，首先要對方有人權。香港人老早把人權丢掉，根本無法被侵犯。更有人自甘被圈養如禽畜。根據儒家思想，「無是非之心，非人也。」非人也，何論人權？<br />\n<br />\n所以，袁國勇大概說對了。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔係比販民共狗強姦開<br />\n撚有人權<br />\n佢地係好應該走去驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59711c1779afdef3c5b6827db50495a5f6448974","tid":2293661,"uid":381265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:15:48.000Z","msg":"袁狗"},{"pid":"15f98cd7465587d23e4258765d27b240569a715b","tid":2293661,"uid":5721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog